<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Attention-deficit_hyperactivity_disorder&amp;action=edit&amp;section=41" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ul>
<li>Barkley, Russell A. <i>Take Charge of ADHD: The Complete Authoritative Guide for Parents</i> (2005) New York: Guilford Publications.</li>
<li>Conrad, Peter <i>Identifying Hyperactive Children</i> (Ashgate, 2006).</li>
